headline: PG&E Q3 Earnings Surpass Estimates, Revenues Increase Y/Y
summary: PCG's third-quarter total revenues of $5.94 billion rise 0.9% from the year-ago level. Operating revenues, however, lag the Zacks Consensus Estimate by 10.9%.
